abstract: Cisco Systems, the computer networking giant that has been on a bit of a shopping spree of late, supplied more evidence that technology sales were recovering along with the global economy.

lead_paragraph: Cisco Systems, the computer networking giant that has been on a bit of a shopping spree of late, supplied more evidence on Wednesday that technology sales were recovering along with the global economy.

headline.main: Solid Results for One Dealmaker: Cisco
